2) Programmatically 컬럼 select form 만들기

paragraphs.text:
val columns = spark.table("survey").columns
val numBins = z.textbox("막대 개수", "10").toString
val selected = z.select("컬럼", columns(0), columns.map(x => (x, x)))

// NOTE: 여기서 ${...}은 zeppelin의 dynamic form이 아니라, scala의 string interpolation임
z.show(sql(s"""
WITH
target (
SELECT ${selected} AS x
FROM survey
WHERE ${selected} IS NOT NULL
),
stats (
SELECT
    MIN(x) AS x_min,
    MAX(x) - MIN(x) AS x_range,
    ${numBins} AS num_bins
FROM target
),
bin (
SELECT
    x,
    FLOOR((x - x_min) / (x_range / num_bins)) AS bin
FROM
    target
    CROSS JOIN stats
)
SELECT
    CASE WHEN bin = num_bins THEN num_bins - 1 ELSE bin END AS bin,
    COUNT(*) AS bin_cnt,
    AVG(x) AS bin_avg,
    MIN(x) AS bin_min,
    MAX(x) AS bin_max
FROM
    bin
    CROSS JOIN stats
GROUP BY 1
ORDER BY 1 
"""))

    val selectedColumn = z.select("컬럼", numericalColumns(0), numericalColumns.map(x => (x, x)))
    
    z.angularBind("numBins", numBins) // Override the dynamic form "numBins".

%sql
WITH
target (
SELECT ${column} AS x
FROM survey
WHERE ${column} IS NOT NULL
),
stats (
SELECT
    MIN(x) AS x_min,
    ${numBins} AS num_bins,
    (MAX(x) - MIN(x)) / ${numBins} AS bin_width
FROM target
),
bin_tmp (
SELECT
    x,
    FLOOR((x - x_min) / bin_width) AS bin
FROM target CROSS JOIN stats
),
bin (
SELECT
    x,
    CASE WHEN bin = num_bins THEN num_bins - 1 ELSE bin END AS bin  -- 마지막 bin의 범위를 90 ~ 99이 아닌 90 ~ 100이 되도록
FROM bin_tmp CROSS JOIN stats
)
SELECT
    bin,
    COUNT(*) AS bin_count,
    AVG(x) AS bin_avg,
    MIN(x) AS bin_min,
    MAX(x) AS bin_max,
    MIN(bin_width) * bin AS bin_start,
    MIN(bin_width) * (bin + 1) AS bin_end
FROM bin CROSS JOIN stats
GROUP BY bin
ORDER BY bin
